      "value": "<p>&gt;@UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.class-features.Item.On2ZrPJTe8FURsXY]{Operative Exploit}</p>\n<p>Once per day, you can use your @UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.class-features.Item.694I7riEDNVucab2]{Mysterious Benefactor (Ex)} exploit to reroll a failed @UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.rules.JournalEntry.GMkLZsN3a7YPvA03.JournalEntryPage.bD4kmdFU7wwsenOf#earn-a-living]{Earn a Living} check, or you can add 5 to your result and use the new value as the result of the check. At the GMâ€™s discretion, this ability can also be used to reroll a Charisma-based skill check when you need a professional to help you, such as when you are disguised as a clerk and need another employee to vouch for your disguise, or when you knock out a bouncer at a club and need a replacement to cover their shift. You must have the Mysterious Benefactor exploit to learn this exploit.</p>"
